instructions: Put the charger in the middle of the table cloth
Place the dinner fork to the left of the charger
place the dinner knife to the right of the charger
place the salad fork to the left of the dinner fork
place the salad knife to the right of the dinner knife
place the soup spoon to the right of the salad knife
Place the dessert spoon horizontally above the charger with the bowl pointed left
place the dessert fork horizontally below the dessert spoon with the prong pointed right
place the bread plate above the salad fork
place the butter knife on the bread plate diagonally with the blade to the top left
place the water glass above the salad knife
place the napkin on the plate
